{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abaa7dbee2","title":"给文炳障的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"029d8d4fda","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"abaa7dbee2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"01a0a93b02","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文炳琼，毛泽东的表径。毛泽荣，又名逊五，毛泽东的堂弟。毛仙梅，毛泽东的堂弟。"},{"id":"17d9ffa336","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文梅清、文东仙，毛泽东的表弟。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e9ea378af9","type":"title","text":"给文炳境的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"},{"id":"01a0a93b02","type":"paragraph","text":"炳障同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"},{"id":"17d9ffa336","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十五日的信收到。你可去找毛泽荣（逊五）毛仙梅二人，和他们一道来京一行，即持此信为证。其他各人均不要来。请你转告文梅清、文东仙问二同志，他们给我的信收到了，他们的问题我不能解决，他们不要来京。韶山方面有要来的，除泽荣、仙梅二人可以来之外，均不可来。问你母亲及各位朋友的好！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"},{"id":"7a5909ec78","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"},{"id":"21ea2bced6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年五月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"},{"id":"4ddbd117ef","type":"paragraph","text":"此信给毛泽荣、毛仙梅二人一阅。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2"}],"page":{"id":"e80595f994","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"abaa7dbee2","start":60,"end":60}}}},"__N_SSG":true}